data.description: Reduced! Motivated Seller, assignable VA loan. Don't miss this almost new 4 bedroom, 3 bath, ranch. Amazing Ranch with an Open Floorplan and walkout basement, kitchen with oversized island, and walk-in pantry, Stainless steel appliances, gas range, tile backsplash, white cabinets. Vinyl plank flooring throughout entry, great room, kitchen and nook. This home is perfect for one floor living, with all bedrooms on the main level. Unfinished basement is ready for finishing, for an additional floor of living space. Enjoy the covered patio and fenced backyard with over $30k in landscaping, perfect for entertaining. Great family neighborhood! Don't miss this one.
